query:
SELECT 
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wl.locationType,
  wz.name as zoneName,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  SUM(i.quantity) as totalQuantity
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
LEFT JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
WHERE i.quantity > 0
GROUP BY wl.code, wl.locationType, wz.name, wz.code
LIMIT 10;
